      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZOURRIFIC (6) two-year-old Zoustar gelding from Glamorize on debut for the Peter Snowden stable. Takes on the older horse after impressing in his two latest trial wins. Tongue-tie goes on and expected to go close. ROYAL AIR FORCE (3) frustrating type gelded over the break. Primed for this with the two sound trials and gets every chance to break through from the inside gate. SHORT SEA (5) is a two-year-old colt by Ole Kirk from Steamboat Sally also on debut for the Peter Snowden stable. Has shown promise in all his trials and gets map favours with the winkers going on. POWER HUNGRY (8) twelve-start Maiden who can sneak into the placings with the 3kg claim. Came out quickly in the heavy (10) going and did well to secure third over 1100m at Nowra. Can surprise with race fitness on his side.",
